Recognition is always appreciated. When I started my career as a banker I found myself as the #2 banker in the company and the nation. Now as I have made several transitions in my career to being a Mortgage Officer and getting the opportunity to help people buy and refinance their homes I find myself receiving a similar award. Being one of the Top Mortgage officers in country allows me to receive US Bank's highest honor #legendsofpossible award. The truth is it really does not happen with out the team I have around me and the circle of people I keep close to my chest.

It's truly amazing for me to receive this award but I am even more grateful to those people that helped drive and build my success.

I am not sales guy, just doesn't fit me but I am a solutions guy. I find ways everyday to improve people's lives and as long as I continue to do that, awards or not I think I'll be ok.

Thank you US Bank,
Thank you colleagues,
Thank you peers,
Thank you my friends & family.
